data.description: Discover your coastal dream at 252 Majorca Rd.! This 2017 double-wide mobile home offers a beachy paradise. This 3-bedroom gem is completed with its walk-in closet in each bedroom. The sellers are even sweetening the deal with a $5,000 credit for buyers, the home is being sold As-Is. For a comprehensive list of features, be sure to check the feature list, highlighting the impressive details of this amazing property.   Nestled along the tranquil marshlands, picture yourself waking up to awe-inspiring sunrises overlooking the Frank Butler County Park West and the lush nature preserve. Here, playful native birds become your daily companions, adding a touch of coastal charm. With high tide, embark on stand-up paddleboarding or kayaking adventures right from your backyard. As the day concludes, witness the sky turning into a canvas of warm, vibrant colors during mesmerizing sunsets.  This secluded coastal haven not only offers a beautiful home but a whole lifestyle. A private community beach walkover grants you easy access to the pristine white sands of Butler Beach. Nearby, you'll find delightful dining options at fantastic restaurants like Back 40 A1A, Violas, and Elkhouse Eatery, perfect for leisurely walks or bike rides. The voluntary HOA in the neighborhood adds to the charm of this beachy paradise. Looking for an investment opportunity? This property can serve as a lucrative short-term vacation rental. Elevated comfortably at 10.5 feet, it ensures your coastal haven remains dry and secure. With spacious interiors, a robust foundation, and outdoor delights like a screened-in porch, fire pit, and marsh-view wooden deck, this property embodies the essence of beachy living. Sellers are in the process of moving new photos coming soon! Don't let this coastal gem slip through your fingers!
